data.description: Only four blocks from Buckeye Lake. Located in the Fairfield Beach area. Three bedroom, two full baths, mobile home, nestled in a quite setting. This home offers an open floor plan, walk in closets, 2 x 6 walls, fully dry-walled. New roof and A/C unit. Carport, off street parking. 200-amp electrical service. Outdoor shed. Kitchen appliances to remain.
